    <p>
        - The solvent front is 10.5cm from the starting line.<br>
        - Yellow is 2cm from the starting line.<br>
        - Purple is 6.5cm from the starting line.<br>
        - Blue is 9cm from the starting line.<br>
        - <b>Using the R<sub>f</sub> equation:</b>
        <ul>
            <li>Yellow: R<sub>f</sub> = 2/10.5 = 0.19</li>
            <li>Purple: R<sub>f</sub> = 6.5/10.5 = 0.62</li>
            <li>Blue: R<sub>f</sub> = 9/10.5 = 0.86</li>
        </ul>
    </p>
